As the tension escalates over the death of Iranian top military brass, Suleimani killed by the U.S. by a drone strike, Iran vowed to retaliate. Early today, the American embassy in Iraq was hit by an airstrike killing many, including American soldiers. The picture of an Ameican named Mitch Mayfield surfaced online. A twitter user had posted the picture slamming President Trump for starting crisis in the Middle East that claimed the lives of soldiers and civilians. According to him, he wished black people in America would stop enlisting in the army. America has vowed punishment.